Magnet Mobile API for Android

Packages 
Package Description
com.magnet.android.mms
Top level package containing the starting class for initializing the Magnet Mobile Server library for Android.
com.magnet.android.mms.async
Provides classes for creating and managing asynchronous calls.
com.magnet.android.mms.async.constraint
Provides constraint classes for managing asynchronous calls.
com.magnet.android.mms.async.tag
Provides an interface and classes for tagging asynchronous calls.
com.magnet.android.mms.connection
Provides interfaces and classes for configuring Magnet Mobile Server backend profiles.
com.magnet.android.mms.controller
Provides the parent class needed by generated controllers for making method calls to a Magnet Mobile Server backend.
com.magnet.android.mms.exception
Provides exception classes.
com.magnet.android.mms.settings
Provides classes for configuring Magnet applications.
com.magnet.android.mms.utils
Provides utility classes for Android-related actions.
com.magnet.android.mms.utils.logger
Provides classes for storing diagnostic messages in the Android log.
